title: 721 Dao direction
body:
1: Community DAO only. Where only VIP(OG) can participate by committing ETH in exchange for DAO NFT where it can be traded in Opensea.
We use the Dao to purchase NFT or mint. Might fractionize some good 1/1.

2: Dual DAO.  Community DAO + Closed DAO
Community Dao does not commit any ETH. 
Closed DAO is invited only and can form a bigger pool that gives 1% to community DAO for free.

Please take this under serious consideration as it can turn out very differently for our members and early core contributor like me where I will be committing most of my time into 721DAO.

9x9x9
